<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-14701] Cleanup (and other) compaction type(s) not counted in compaction remaining time</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14701</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Opened a ticket, as discussed in user list.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looks like compaction remaining time only includes compactions of type COMPACTION and other compaction types like cleanup etc. aren&apos;t part of the estimation calculation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;E.g. from one of our environments:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;nodetool compactionstats -H

pending tasks: 1
   compaction type   keyspace           table   completed     total    unit   progress
           Cleanup        XXX             YYY   908.16 GB   1.13 TB   bytes     78.63%
Active compaction remaining time :   0h00m00s
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
